"8BitDo %@ — set the S/D mode switch" = "8BitDo %@ — 設定 S/D 模式開關";
"Slide the bottom **mode switch to D** (D-input) so it pairs as an 8BitDo %@, then turn it on — an LED blinks." = "將底部的**模式開關撥到 D**（D-input），使其以 8BitDo %@ 配對，然後開機——指示燈會閃爍。";
"Hold the **Pair button** (next to the USB-C port) for ~3 seconds, until the LED blinks rapidly." = "按住**Pair 按鈕**（USB-C 埠旁）約 3 秒，直到指示燈快速閃爍。";
"Connect to **8BitDo %@** under Nearby Devices." = "在附近的裝置中連接 **8BitDo %@**。";
"Bottom switch: **D** = D-input/Android (pairs as an *8BitDo %@*, matching this layout); **S** = Switch mode (pairs as a *Switch Pro Controller*). Both work with ControllerKeys." = "底部開關：**D** = D-input/Android（以 *8BitDo %@* 配對，與此佈局相符）；**S** = Switch 模式（以 *Switch Pro Controller* 配對）。兩者均可在 ControllerKeys 中使用。";

/* Apple TV Siri Remote */
"Pair Your Siri Remote" = "配對 Siri Remote";
"Apple TV Siri Remote (2nd or 3rd gen)" = "Apple TV Siri Remote（第 2 代或第 3 代）";
"If you have an Apple TV nearby, **unplug it first** — the remote has to disconnect from the Apple TV before it can pair to your Mac." = "如果附近有 Apple TV，請**先拔掉它的電源**——遙控器必須先與 Apple TV 中斷連接，才能與你的 Mac 配對。";
"On the remote, hold **Volume Up (+) and the Back button** together until it enters pairing mode." = "在遙控器上，同時按住**Volume Up (+) 和 Back 按鈕**，直到進入配對模式。";
"Select the remote under **Nearby Devices** to connect — it joins as a Bluetooth HID device." = "在**附近的裝置**中選擇遙控器進行連接——它會作為藍牙 HID 裝置加入。";
"Keep the Apple TV unplugged for the whole pairing process so the remote doesn't reconnect to it mid-pair." = "在整個配對過程中保持 Apple TV 斷電，以免遙控器在配對中途重新連接到它。";
